{
  "id": "69b6296337296c16ee2ac104",
  "title": "ゆるトーク:悪質なデマサイト",
  "created": 1773545856,
  "updated": 1773577605,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69b6296337296c16ee2ac104",
      "text": "ゆるトーク:悪質なデマサイト",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545856,
      "updated": 1773545856
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629800000000000a96dcd",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545856,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96dce",
      "text": "やっほー！今日は「[悪質なデマサイト]」についてゆるっと鼎談してくよ～。SNSとか見てるとさ、「え、それマジ？」みたいな記事バズってることあるじゃん。ああいうの、だいたいヤバいやつなんよね。いわゆる“フェイクニュース量産機”。ネット民的には「釣りサイト」って呼ばれたりもするやつ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96dcf",
      "text": "というわけで、まずは基本から！デマサイトって何なの？ってとこ、りか先生よろしく～。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96dd0",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96dd1",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96dd2",
      "text": "了解。簡潔に定義する。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96dd3",
      "text": "悪質なデマサイトとは、事実確認を行わず、または意図的に虚偽の情報を掲載し、アクセス数や広告収益、政治的影響力などを得ることを目的とするWebサイトのこと。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96dd4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96dd5",
      "text": "典型的な特徴を挙げる。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96dd6",
      "text": "　1. [扇動的な見出し]（[クリックベイト]）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773564707
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96dd7",
      "text": "  例：「専門家が警告！○○は今すぐやめろ」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96dd8",
      "text": " 2. [出典が不明確]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773564197
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96dd9",
      "text": "  「[関係者によると]」「[海外研究で判明]」など曖昧。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773564540
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96dda",
      "text": " 3. [広告が多い]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773564641
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96ddb",
      "text": "  PV（ページビュー）を稼いで[広告収益]を得る構造。",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773546835
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96ddc",
      "text": " 4. [感情を強く刺激する内容]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773577605
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96ddd",
      "text": "  [怒り]、[恐怖]、[優越感]など。",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773546846
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96dde",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96ddf",
      "text": "[エビデンス]としては、例えば総務省の資料。",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773546775
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96de0",
      "text": "https://www.soumu.go.jp/main_content/000708217.pdf",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96de1",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96de2",
      "text": "要点をまとめると、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96de3",
      "text": "「お金・影響力・拡散力」を目的に嘘が拡散される構造だ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96de4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96de5",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96de6",
      "text": "うわ～、やっぱ広告マネー問題か～。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96de7",
      "text": "要するに「炎上でも何でもいいからクリックしてくれ！」ってやつだよね。完全に“アクセス乞食”じゃん。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96de8",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96de9",
      "text": "あやはどう思う？SNSとか見てて「これは怪しいなぁ」って感じることある？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96dea",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96deb",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96dec",
      "text": "ええ、ございますね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96ded",
      "text": "ときどき、本を読んでおりますと、まるで古い怪談のように、人の不安や好奇心を巧みに利用した文章に出会うことがありますの。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96dee",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96def",
      "text": "たとえば、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96df0",
      "text": "「今すぐこの食べ物をやめないと危険」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96df1",
      "text": "「医者が隠している真実」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96df2",
      "text": "そういった言葉は、まるで人の心を軽く揺さぶる鈴の音のようでして……つい目を留めてしまいます。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96df3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96df4",
      "text": "ですが、よく読みますと、誰が語ったのかが分からないのです。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96df5",
      "text": "それは、物語としては面白くても、事実としてはとても頼りないものですわね。（微笑）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96df6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96df7",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96df8",
      "text": "あ～わかる！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96df9",
      "text": "「医者も驚いた！」とか「世界が震撼！」とか、主語デカすぎ問題あるよねｗ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96dfa",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96dfb",
      "text": "しかもさ、だいたい記事の最後が",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96dfc",
      "text": "「詳しくはこちらのサプリで！」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96dfd",
      "text": "とかで終わるやつｗ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96dfe",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96dff",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96e00",
      "text": "典型的な[アフィリエイト誘導]だ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773558599
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96e01",
      "text": "構造を説明する。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96e02",
      "text": " 1. デマ記事を作る",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96e03",
      "text": " 2. SNSで拡散",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96e04",
      "text": " 3. 不安を煽る",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96e05",
      "text": " 4. 商品リンクへ誘導",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96e06",
      "text": "このモデルは[コンテンツマーケティング]の悪用と言える。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773558593
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96e07",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96e08",
      "text": "ちなみに海外では研究も多い。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96e09",
      "text": "MITの研究では、偽ニュースは真実より約6倍速く拡散すると報告されている。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96e0a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96e0b",
      "text": "https://www.science.org/doi/10.1126/science.aap9559",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96e0c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96e0d",
      "text": "理由はシンプル。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96e0e",
      "text": "驚き・怒り・恐怖の情報は人がシェアしやすい。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96e0f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96e10",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96e11",
      "text": "6倍！？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96e12",
      "text": "うわ、それ完全にバグってるじゃんネット社会。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96e13",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96e14",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96e15",
      "text": "人は、驚くことや怖いことに出会うと、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96e16",
      "text": "「誰かに知らせなければ」と思ってしまうのでしょうね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96e17",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96e18",
      "text": "まるで昔、村に怪しい噂が流れたときのように……。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96e19",
      "text": "噂は、風に乗って遠くまで届いてしまいます。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96e1a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96e1b",
      "text": "ですが、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96e1c",
      "text": "優しさから広めた情報が、誰かを傷つけてしまうこともある。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96e1d",
      "text": "それは、とても悲しいことですわね。（静かに微笑）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96e1e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96e1f",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96e20",
      "text": "あや、それめっちゃ本質じゃん……。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96e21",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96e22",
      "text": "「善意のRT」がデマ拡散って、よくあるんだよね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96e23",
      "text": "しかも最近はAI画像とかもあるし、もう見分ける難易度ハードモード。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96e24",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96e25",
      "text": "りか、そのへんどう対策すればいいの？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96e26",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96e27",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96e28",
      "text": "基本は3ステップ検証。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96e29",
      "text": " 1. ソース確認",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96e2a",
      "text": "  元記事や公式発表があるか。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96e2b",
      "text": " 2. 複数メディア確認",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96e2c",
      "text": "  信頼できる媒体（新聞・研究機関）で報じられているか。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96e2d",
      "text": " 3. 日付確認",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96e2e",
      "text": "  古いニュースが再拡散されているケースが多い。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96e2f",
      "text": "参考として、ファクトチェック団体もある。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96e30",
      "text": "日本ファクトチェックセンター",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96e31",
      "text": "https://www.factcheckcenter.jp/",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96e32",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96e33",
      "text": "要点を整理する。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96e34",
      "text": " デマサイトは感情を煽る",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96e35",
      "text": " 収益モデルは広告・アフィリエイト",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96e36",
      "text": " 対策は情報源の確認",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96e37",
      "text": "[情報リテラシー]は、現代の必須スキルだ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773558633
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96e38",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96e39",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96e3a",
      "text": "さすが技術担当、まとめがプロｗ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96e3b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96e3c",
      "text": "でもさ～、個人的に一番ヤバいと思うのは、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96e3d",
      "text": "デマを信じてる人同士で固まる現象なんよね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96e3e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96e3f",
      "text": "なんていうか…",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96e40",
      "text": "「このサイトだけが真実！」みたいな。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96e41",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96e42",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96e43",
      "text": "それは[エコーチェンバー現象]と呼ばれる。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773558649
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96e44",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96e45",
      "text": "同じ意見の人だけが集まり、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96e46",
      "text": "意見が増幅される現象。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96e47",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96e48",
      "text": "SNSアルゴリズムがそれを強化することもある。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96e49",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96e4a",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96e4b",
      "text": "同じ声ばかりが響く部屋……",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96e4c",
      "text": "まるで山の谷間のこだまのようですわね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96e4d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96e4e",
      "text": "自分の言葉が返ってくるだけでは、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96e4f",
      "text": "新しい景色は見えませんもの。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96e50",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96e51",
      "text": "時には、違う風の音にも耳を傾けたいものです。（微笑）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96e52",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96e53",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96e54",
      "text": "あや、詩人すぎるｗ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96e55",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96e56",
      "text": "じゃあ最後にまとめいくよ～。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96e57",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96e58",
      "text": "今日のポイント！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96e59",
      "text": " デマサイトはクリック稼ぎや影響力目的",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96e5a",
      "text": " 感情を煽る記事は要注意",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96e5b",
      "text": " ソース確認＆複数チェック大事",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96e5c",
      "text": " SNSではデマが爆速で広がる",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96e5d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96e5e",
      "text": "つまり…",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96e5f",
      "text": "「バズってる＝本当」じゃない！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96e60",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96e61",
      "text": "ネット民のみんな、RTする前に3秒だけ疑おう。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96e62",
      "text": "それだけで世界のデマ、ちょっと減るかも！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b65dcb00000000007e07fa",
      "text": " できないことが証明され続けている...[基素.icon]",
      "userId": "59fb21121207900012774b17",
      "created": 1773559244,
      "updated": 1773559254
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96e63",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96e64",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96e65",
      "text": "合理的な結論だ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96e66",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96e67",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96e68",
      "text": "ええ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96e69",
      "text": "疑うことは冷たいことではなく、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96e6a",
      "text": "真実を大切にするための優しさなのかもしれませんね。（静かに笑う）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96e6b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96e6c",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96e6d",
      "text": "おお～きれいに締まった！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b629810000000000a96e6e",
      "text": "じゃあ今日はこのへんで～。またね～！ 🎮",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545857,
      "updated": 1773545857
    },
    {
      "id": "69b62a0f0000000000a96e75",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773545999,
      "updated": 1773545999
    },
    {
      "id": "69b62a0f0000000000a96e76",
      "text": "#2026-03-15",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773546000,
      "updated": 1773546011
    },
    {
      "id": "69b62a110000000000a96e77",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773546001,
      "updated": 1773546001
    }
  ]
}